            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Loyalty Discount</h3>
          <p>Exclusive pricing for Xclear Networks customers. Ask about our bundled service packages.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>
          <p>We already know your infrastructure. AI deployment is faster because we understand your environment.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Single Point of Contact</h3>
          <p>One team for networks AND AI automation. Simplify your vendor relationships.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="use-cases">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>AI Solutions That Complement Your Network</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Maximize the value of your technology investment</p>
      
      <div class="use-cases-grid">
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Email & Communication</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Let AI triage your inbox, draft responses, and manage calendar scheduling while your network keeps everything connected.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Security Monitoring</h3>
          </div>
          <p>AI-powered alerts that work with your network monitoring to catch issues before they become problems.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M8.625 12a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H8.25m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0H12m4.125 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm0 0h-.375M21 12c0 4.556-4.03 8.25-9 8.25a9.764 9.764 0 01-2.555-.337A5.972 5.972 0 015.41 20.97a5.969 5.969 0 01-.474-.065 4.48 4.48 0 00.978-2.025c.09-.457-.133-.901-.467-1.226C3.93 16.178 3 14.189 3 12c0-4.556 4.03-8.25 9-8.25s9 3.694 9 8.25z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Customer Service</h3>
          </div>
          <p>24/7 AI support that handles inquiries instantly, escalating to humans only when needed.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Business Intelligence</h3>
          </div>
          <p>AI that synthesizes data from across your connected systems into actionable insights.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Workflow Automation</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Eliminate manual data entry and repetitive tasks across your networked applications.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="use-case">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Multi-Location Support</h3>
          </div>
          <p>AI assistants that work across all your connected sites, providing consistent service everywhere.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimonial">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"We've trusted Xclear Networks with our infrastructure for years. When they introduced AI automation, it was a natural fit. Same great team, now with even more capability."</p>
        <cite>â€” Xclear Networks Customer</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-container">
      <h2>Ready to Add AI to Your Technology Stack?</h2>
      <p>As a valued Xclear Networks customer, you're already ahead of the curve. Let's talk about how AI can take your business to the next level.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Schedule Your Demo</a>
        <a href="tel:3853366005" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Call (385) 336-6005</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gradient-start) 0%, var(--bg-primary) 100%);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #dcfce7;
    border: 1px solid #86efac;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #166534;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  [data-theme="dark"] .hero-badge {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    color: #34d399;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .btn {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }
  
  .btn-lg {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .section-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  /* Transition Section */
  .transition {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .timeline-item {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 350px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .timeline-icon {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
  }
  
  .timeline-icon svg {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .timeline-arrow svg {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .timeline-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .timeline-arrow svg {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  
  /* Benefits Section */
  .benefits {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .benefit-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  
  .benefit-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  
  .benefit-card.highlight {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    border-color: var(--accent-border);
  }
  
  .benefit-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
  }
  
  .benefit-icon svg {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .benefit-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  /* Use Cases Section */
  .use-cases {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .use-cases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .use-case {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .use-case-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .use-case-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #6366f1 100%);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .use-case-icon svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .use-case h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .use-case p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  
  /* Testimonial */
  .testimonial {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  blockquote {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  blockquote p {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  cite {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--gradient-start) 100%);
    text-align: center;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .cta-container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .cta-container p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .timeline-arrow svg {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }
</style>
</Layout>
